# Ignore atomic-write temp files so `shopify theme dev` / `theme push` don't try
# to sync them. Editors and Claude Code save files by writing
# "<name>.tmp.<pid>.<hash>" then renaming — the watcher can catch the temp file
# mid-write and error: '… .tmp.… contains illegal characters'. These never belong
# in the theme.
*.tmp.*
*/*.tmp.*
sections/*.tmp.*
snippets/*.tmp.*
assets/*.tmp.*
layout/*.tmp.*
templates/*.tmp.*
config/*.tmp.*
locales/*.tmp.*

# Editor swap/backup files
*~
*.swp
*.bak
